on.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage ","bodyContent":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","toRecipients":"={{ $json.email || 'ops@company.com' }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOutlook","typeVersion":2,"position":[5157,1420],"id":"87477933-19ff-43f8-bd08-2d498d3373d3","name":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hourly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — every 4 h. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Post","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"0376a761-664e-c482-251c-a6debb9d8075","name":"Note: Hourly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Post\n\nShapes the item: writes `postId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"4bff33a3-629e-3f98-b761-7648bd64d374","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Post"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.postId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Classify with AI · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"6bf22305-3193-6897-eda2-d3e9bcd3cb92","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"4b68ec21-0561-c82c-ea5e-2545348d8da2","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Classify with AI\n\nLLM classification into: Mention, Question, Complaint (+fallback). Output port order matches this list.\n\nPorts: ①→ Store as Mention · ②→ Store as Question, Capture Failure Context · ③→ Store as Complaint · ④→ Alert Slack — Other\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"bea83113-c66c-fcfe-40bf-3d3d97719526","name":"Note: Classify with AI"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenRouter Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Classify with AI** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenRouter API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1090],"id":"5a431aa0-7dc4-70cc-5b0f-131d0e574cd3","name":"Note: OpenRouter Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Mention\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,40],"id":"5760206f-500a-8b90-d26b-9e02d9afa9d8","name":"Note: Store as Mention"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Question\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,490],"id":"b28fd935-30b6-dd3b-237b-2c12e03807a5","name":"Note: Store as Question"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Complaint\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,940],"id":"b7366ac2-6924-3428-8eda-f411df407e05","name":"Note: Store as Complaint"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Alert Slack — Other\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2181,1390],"id":"31bb9181-d00d-dd87-4a5e-8df247a9cb15","name":"Note: Alert Slack — Other"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Reunite Branches\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty content","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2829,520],"id":"ac8fb99c-9dbe-711d-13d6-fa88980e8b98","name":"Note: Reunite Branches"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty content\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Sort Posts Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"25fb57f3-2ee7-8888-e939-b6b69eff052e","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty content"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Posts Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"1be532e0-04e4-efd3-3c94-225bf83e753b","name":"Note: Sort Posts Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,520],"id":"2f19ce63-791d-3219-5877-dbc115ad2ea2","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,520],"id":"cd8b7189-e9ce-62c8-6a33-fb6b19368b47","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Outlook · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5097,520],"id":"7f174545-da8d-480f-5bc7-ad3f902f5d3c","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5421,520],"id":"8c87f11d-d76f-6991-6223-613f5fe0d653","name":"Note: Send Summary to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Outlook","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,1540],"id":"fd0f10e7-cbcf-fc0a-d4e1-764bb5f5ee37","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5097,1540],"id":"62e3e059-9818-68f9-e7b6-9a3bc5a86082","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Listen for keywords with HTTP / REST API and Outlook hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** Social Listening · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nListen for keywords with HTTP / REST API and Outlook hands-free. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual listening is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule → Stamp & Shape Post → Payload Valid? → Classify with AI → Store as Mention → Reunite Branches → Guard Non-Empty content → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to social listening without manual effort\n- Anyone automating listening in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Responds in seconds\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; OpenRouter API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"efeb2e8a-5a89-7784-32dc-5d1f7ceba700","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"acf3eefa-2a92-ed0d-363d-5810d28575fe","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"a0990707-99b8-80a8-a42c-f2e6cb9a87a1","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your listening process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"be198ceb-97f6-0e7b-0706-c767dec6e430","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Hourly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Post","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Post":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Classify with AI","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenRouter Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Classify with AI","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Classify with AI":{"main":[[{"node":"Store as Mention","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Store as Question","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Store as Complaint","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Alert Slack — Other","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Mention":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Question":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Complaint":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Alert Slack — Other":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Reunite Branches":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty content","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty content":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Posts Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Posts Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Outlook":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"e0782cbe-4cd6-4680-a44a-84e89ef6d75d","id":"FDX06967"}